 the minor axis is traced back to\ndeformation-aligned orbits.\n  Conclusions: The NLF allows a simple interpretation of the shell structure\nevolution in the rotating nucleus in terms of the angular-momentum alignment of\nindividual nucleons. We expect that the NLF will be useful for the\ncharacterization of other collective modes and time-dependent processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2020 03:50:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Aug 2020 05:38:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 23:30:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-09"}
