cture\nexperiments on a modern ultra-high strength steel, AerMet100. A promising\nagreement is observed with experimental measurements of threshold stress\nintensity factor $K_{th}$ over a wide range of applied potentials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2020 15:14:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-15"}
